articles.title: Female motorcyclist, 33, dies after colliding with lorry on PIE
articles.content: A 33-year-old female motorcyclist died after colliding with a lorry on the Pan-Island Expressway (PIE) on Wednesday (Jan 21). She was pronounced dead at the scene, SCDF added. The police said that the 40-year-old male lorry driver is assisting with investigations
